  Add another addpredict location, closed bug 126667

  17 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> totem-1.4.0.ebuild:
  Get rid of a spurious 'i' in the ebuild, thanks to Jose daLuz in bug #126469.

